headline: Smurfit Westrock to Announce 2025 Fourth Quarter and Full Year Results together with a Medium-Term investor update on February 11, 2026
summary: DUBLIN, January 26, 2026--Smurfit Westrock plc (NYSE:SW; LSE:SWR) plans to release its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year ended December 31, 2025 together with an update for investors on its Medium-Term Plan, capital allocation priorities and value drivers on Wednesday, February 11, 2026 at approximately 6:30 am ET (11:30 am GMT). Smurfit Westrock’s earnings release and related materials as well as its investor update presentation will be available at smurfitwestrock.com.
